      "order": 1,
      "Description": "This lesson explores the risks that arise when artificial intelligence tools are used to create brand messaging, and why those risks matter for businesses of all sizes. You will learn how AI-generated content can miss the mark on tone, produce factual inaccuracies, and inadvertently cause reputational damage if left unchecked. We will look at real-world examples of where things have gone wrong, and what warning signs to watch out for before publishing AI-assisted content. By the end of the lesson, you will have a clearer understanding of how to use AI writing tools responsibly, with the right level of human oversight in place. No prior technical knowledge is required, just an interest in protecting your brand and communicating with confidence.",
