          "slidecontent": "• AI can mimic your brand voice but cannot guarantee accuracy or contextual judgement\n\n• Always review AI-generated copy before it goes anywhere near your audience\n\n• Tone mismatches and factual errors are the two biggest risks to watch for\n\n• Unchecked AI output can quietly erode trust\n\n• Build a simple approval step into your workflow to catch problems early\n\n• Start small, test outputs against your brand guidelines, and adjust from there"
